When I added the images and added it to my client it showed a bunch of blank images when you scrolled over it, it would say the emote and you could still click it. That should be all. If there's anything else I'll just post in here some more. OH THE LAST THING IS THAT NPC'S KEEP ON GLITCHING. WHEN YOU KILL AN NPC THEY LIKE SHAKE OR SOMETHING. CAN SOMEONE PLEASE SHOW ME HOW TO FIX THIS OR W/E.
